OL,3,CWelsh Government reading expert quits,
OL,4,Cwarning #8.2m plan 'not fit for
OL,5,Cpurpose'
OL,7,FThe Welsh Government's plans to raise
OL,8,Freading standards have been thrown
OL,9,Finto doubt after a key member of its
OL,10,Fexpert literacy panel resigned,
OL,11,Faccusing ministers of embedding "mixed
OL,12,Fmessages" into a new #8.2 million
OL,13,Fscheme to improve literacy.
OL,15,FThe panel was created in response to
OL,16,FITV News' investigation last year,
OL,17,Fwhich exposed serious flaws in the way
OL,18,Freading is taught in Welsh schools.
