OL,4,Cwarning #8.2m plan 'not fit for
OL,5,Cpurpose'
OL,7,FElizabeth Nonweiler, one of only two
OL,8,Fmembers of the panel with experience
OL,9,Fteaching children to read, told ITV
OL,10,FNews the group has achieved nothing in
OL,11,Fnearly a year and that its failings
OL,12,Fare now being built into the
OL,13,Fgovernment's new national literacy
OL,14,Fprogramme.
OL,16,F"After a year of meetings, I realised
OL,17,Fwe weren't going to produce statements
OL,18,Fthat clearly describe the best way to
OL,19,Fteach early reading, according to
OL,20,Fresearch and experience," she said.
