OL,7,FWriting to the Cabinet Secretary for
OL,8,FEducation, Lynne Neagle, she has
OL,9,Fwarned that the government's current
OL,10,Fplans "will fail unless they change
OL,11,Fdirection."
OL,13,FITV News has approached the Welsh
OL,14,Fgovernment for comment.
OL,16,FAnybody's guess
OL,18,FAt the heart of the row is an old
OL,19,Fquestion: how should children be
OL,20,Ftaught to read?
