OL,7,FMajor national reviews - including the
OL,8,FUK's Rose Review (2006) and the US
OL,9,FNational Reading Panel - have each
OL,10,Ffound that systematic synthetic
OL,11,Fphonics offers the most reliable
OL,12,Ffoundation for early reading.
OL,14,FThe method teaches children the sounds
OL,15,Fletters represent and how to blend
OL,16,Fthem into words, an approach backed by
OL,17,Fdecades of research and credited with
OL,18,Fhelping England rise sharply in
OL,19,Finternational literacy rankings since
OL,20,F2010.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/28
