OL,7,FIn Wales, however, ITV News has
OL,8,Frepeatedly found schools still using
OL,9,Fso-called "balanced" or "cueing"
OL,10,Fmethods - encouraging pupils to guess
OL,11,Fwords from pictures or context, or
OL,12,Fmemorise them by sight.
OL,14,FThese strategies, long discredited by
OL,15,Fcognitive scientists, can leave many
OL,16,Fchildren struggling to read fluently.
