OL,7,FOur investigation last year uncovered
OL,8,Fhundreds of examples of cueing in
OL,9,Finspection reports and classroom
OL,10,Fmaterials, prompting ministers to
OL,11,Fpromise clearer guidance.
OL,13,FFirst Minister Eluned Morgan told the
OL,14,FSenedd it was vital to "follow
OL,15,Fevidence" and place "more
OL,16,Fconcentration on phonics".
OL,18,FYet almost a year later, the Expert
OL,19,FLiteracy Panel set up in response has
OL,20,Fpublished nothing.
