OL,7,FIts work remains confidential and no
OL,8,Fnew guidance has reached teachers,
OL,9,Fwhile the Welsh Government has
OL,10,Flaunched an #8.2 million literacy
OL,11,Fprogramme that Mrs Nonweiler says
OL,12,Frepeats the same mistakes.
OL,14,FThe panel was set up to lead an
OL,15,F"evidence-based review" into reading
OL,16,Finstruction.
