OL,7,FIt brought together nine members,
OL,8,Fincluding academics from Cambridge,
OL,9,FUCL, York and Bangor University,
OL,10,Falongside Mrs Nonweiler - one of only
OL,11,Ftwo with direct classroom experience
OL,12,Fof teaching early reading.
OL,14,FSince then, there have been regular
OL,15,Fmeetings but no published outcomes or
OL,16,Fminutes.
OL,18,FMrs Nonweiler says she grew
OL,19,Fincreasingly alarmed at how vague and
OL,20,Fbureaucratic the process became.
