OL,7,F"I suggested a simple, straightforward
OL,8,Fdescription of systematic synthetic
OL,9,Fphonics," she told ITV News. "It was
OL,10,Fignored. The documents we were shown
OL,11,Fwere wordy and unclear, perhaps to
OL,12,Favoid exposing the lack of consensus
OL,13,Famong panel members."
OL,15,FShe says the group's work has been
OL,16,F"confusing and lacking in
OL,17,Ftransparency", and that when
OL,18,Fgovernment officials finally briefed
OL,19,Fmembers on the new national programme,
OL,20,Fdetails were "minimal".
