OL,7,FA new literacy programme with old
OL,8,Fproblems
OL,10,FEarlier this month, the Welsh
OL,11,FGovernment announced CAL:ON Cymru, a
OL,12,F"national school for literacy" based
OL,13,Fat Bangor University, funded with #8.2
OL,14,Fmillion over three years.
OL,16,FIt promises professional learning,
OL,17,Ffree classroom materials, and "support
OL,18,Ffor the systematic teaching of
OL,19,Fphonics".
