OL,7,FBut while the announcement refers to
OL,8,F"systematic phonics", it does not use
OL,9,Fthe term "synthetic phonics" - a
OL,10,Fdistinction critics say reflects an
OL,11,Fongoing reluctance to commit fully to
OL,12,Fthe evidence.
OL,14,FMrs Nonweiler warns that the project
OL,15,Fis being led by several of her former
OL,16,Fpanel colleagues, none of whom has
OL,17,Ftaught young children to read, and
OL,18,Fsome of whom have published work
OL,19,Fcritical of synthetic phonics.
