OL,7,F"#6,700 per primary school is enough
OL,8,Fto buy a proven phonics programme with
OL,9,Fmatched resources and training," she
OL,10,Fsaid. "So that every teacher
OL,11,Funderstands how to teach children to
OL,12,Fread."
OL,14,FThe Welsh Government says CAL:ON Cymru
OL,15,F"draws on the work of the Expert
OL,16,FLiteracy Panel" and "includes specific
OL,17,Fsupport for the systematic teaching of
OL,18,Fphonics."
