OL,7,FFor Mrs Nonweiler, the issue is one of
OL,8,Furgency as well as principle.
OL,10,F"Every year of delay affects thousands
OL,11,Fof children," she said. "Without a
OL,12,Fclear, evidence-based approach, the
OL,13,Fgap between those who learn to read
OL,14,Feasily and those who don't will
OL,15,Fcontinue to grow."
OL,17,FThat gap is already visible in
OL,18,Finternational data. In PISA 2022,
OL,19,FWelsh 15-year-olds scored 466 in
OL,20,Freading - below the OECD average and
OL,21,Fwell behind England's 496.
