OL,7,F'Mixed messages'
OL,9,FITV News previously revealed that some
OL,10,Flocal authorities in Wales were
OL,11,Fpromoting programmes that downplay
OL,12,Fsynthetic phonics.
OL,14,FIn Cardiff, teachers were trained in a
OL,15,Fcourse called Rainbow Reading, which
OL,16,Fexplicitly encouraged pupils to use
OL,17,Fpictures and context to guess words.
