OL,7,FAfter our reporting, the council
OL,8,Fconfirmed that Rainbow Reading is no
OL,9,Flonger being used, and said it would
OL,10,Freview its early reading strategy.
OL,12,FBut similar mixed messages have been
OL,13,Fshared by the schools' watchdog Estyn,
OL,14,Fwhose Chief Inspector seemed to
OL,15,Fmisunderstand what cueing is when he
OL,16,Ftold a Senedd committee this year that
OL,17,F"some children need cue-cards".
