OL,7,F"Saying you support synthetic phonics
OL,8,Fisn't enough," she said. "The guidance
OL,9,Fmust be clear, consistent and
OL,10,Funambiguous. It shouldn't be diluted
OL,11,Fby mixed messages."
OL,13,FFor the Cabinet Secretary, the stakes
OL,14,Fare high. She has repeatedly said that
OL,15,F"improving literacy is central to our
OL,16,Fmission to raise standards", but the
OL,17,Fresignation of one of her panel's few
OL,18,Fclassroom practitioners raises fresh
OL,19,Fquestions about how that mission is
OL,20,Fbeing pursued.
