OL,12,FThe government insists its new
OL,13,Fnational programme "will support
OL,14,Fteachers in developing children's
OL,15,Freading skills through phonics."
OL,17,FBut critics like Mrs Nonweiler - and
OL,18,Fevidence uncovered by ITV News -
OL,19,Fsuggest a deeper cultural problem
OL,20,Fwithin Wales' education system.
