OL,7,FMrs Nonweiler believes Wales could
OL,8,Fachieve the same by following the
OL,9,Fevidence.
OL,11,F"Other countries, like New Zealand,
OL,12,Fhave recently adopted synthetic
OL,13,Fphonics as the foundation for teaching
OL,14,Freading and are already seeing
OL,15,Fsuccess," she said. "But that will
OL,16,Fonly happen here if decisions are
OL,17,Fguided by evidence, clarity and a
OL,18,Fcommitment to what works."
