OL,7,FSimilar reforms have taken hold in
OL,8,FAustralia, Canada and parts of the
OL,9,FUSA. In Mississippi, reading scores
OL,10,Frose from near the bottom of US
OL,11,Frankings in 2013 to among the top ten
OL,12,Fby 2024, following legislation
OL,13,Frequiring evidence-based reading
OL,14,Finstruction.
