OL,7,FHaving more background knowledge is
OL,8,Fparticularly beneficial for poorer
OL,9,Freaders, who are able to compensate
OL,10,Ffor their weaker reading skills.
OL,12,FBut Curriculum for Wales places very
OL,13,Flittle emphasis on specific knowledge.
OL,15,FThis means the government doesn't
OL,16,Fspecify what knowledge pupils should
OL,17,Flearn, leaving it up to schools.
OL,19,FWhat happens next?
