OL,7,FThe Expert Literacy Panel is still in
OL,8,Fplace and is expected to meet again
OL,9,Flater this year. But so far, no
OL,10,Freports, minutes or guidance have been
OL,11,Fpublished, and no timetable for
OL,12,Fpublication has been announced.
OL,14,FThe new CAL:ON Cymru centre is due to
OL,15,Fbegin work before Christmas.
OL,17,FFor Mrs Nonweiler, it's a moment of
OL,18,Freckoning.
OL,20,F"This isn't about politics or pride,"
OL,21,Fshe said. "It's about children."
